# Input file for DRIFTORBIT - Version 1.2
# 
#
0.0046487603        s                  - Radial coordinate s
0.0083816581	    M_t		       - Mach number (for single Mach no. run)
1d0                 qi                 - Particle charge / elem. charge
2.014               mi                 - Particle mass / 1u
1d19		    n0		       - particle density
67744564.0          vth		       - thermal velocity
1e-3		    epsmn	       - perturbation amplitude B1/B0 (if pertfile==F)
0		    m		       - poroidal perturbation mode (if pertfile==F)
2 		    n		       - toroidal perturbation mode (if pertfile==F, n>0!)
-1		    mth		       - poloidal canonical mode (for single Mach no. run)
0       	    mthnum	       - poloidal canonical mode count
0d0	    	    Mtmin	       - minimum Mach number
0d0	    	    Mtmax	       - maximum Mach number
0                   Mtnum              - Mach number count
F                   supban             - calculate superbanana plateau
F		    magdrift	       - consider magnetic drift
F		    nopassing	       - neglect passing particles
F		    calcflux	       - calculate flux directly instead via flux-force relation
T		    noshear	       - neglect magnetic shear term with dqds
F		    pertfile	       - read perturbation from file with neo_magfie_pert
F                   odeint             - use ODE integrator for resonance line


